title: Invasion of the Hottie Snatchers
overview: Just when you thought it was safe to go back to the forest…think again! A group of girls search for their lost friend as they film the journey that takes them deep into the forbidden forest of the Bare Wench. Battling extra-terrestrial beings, the girls must band together-surviving only with a few clothes, their good looks and their very big…brains. It is a Close Encounters of the sexy kind!
